for millions of americans it will be a dream 
realized for organizers a logistical nightmare for eight chosen 
cities it will be a time of tumult for nelson mandela simply a 
welcome 
freed in february after 27 years in south african jails mandela 
plans an exultant tour of the united states this month starting 
with a new york tickertape parade and ending with a rally at the 
oakland calif coliseum 
organizers envision gatherings of uncommon size and emotion 
including throngs at yankee stadium in new york tiger stadium in 
detroit and the los angeles coliseum 
were asking that the people come to him said new york 
coordinator jim bell who is overwhelmed with requests for mandela 
appearances 
