support from libya but it also has said us marines will not move 
to support doe who seized power in a bloody coup 10 years ago 
most of the rebels entered liberia from neighboring ivory coast 
in late december they accuse does administration of corruption 
economic mismanagement and human rights abuses 
taylor had been a close aide of doe heading the government 
agency responsible for disbursing public funds he fled the country 
after the liberian leader accused him of stealing 1 million from 
state coffers 
taylor denies the charges but doe says he will not negotiate 
with a criminal 
descendants of freed us slaves founded liberia in 1822 and it 
became black africas first independent country in 1847 
