ina ramirez 23 a sidewalk vendor of used clothing referring to 
fujimori by his nickname that other man is for the rich 
as fujimori has become more aware of his constituency his 
rhetoric has become more populist he promises to simultaneously 
create hundreds of thousands of jobs and sharply cut perus 2000 
percent annual inflation he doesnt say how hell do it 
the winner will inherit an economy ravaged by hyperinflation and 
a bankrupt government paralyzed by strikes 
and in recent years the maoist shining path rebels have spread 
from their mountain stronghold throughout much of peru political 
violence has claimed more than 18500 lives over the past decade 
