valley news lebanon nh on the summit 
soviet president mikhail gorbachevs visit of course has 
provided a wonderful opportunity for analysts to speculate on his 
chances for survival 
such speculation makes for interesting reading but seems to be 
an exercise with less certainty than guessing next weeks weather 
whatever transpires gorbachevs visit serves as a reminder of 
how much he has already accomplished 
one can criticize him on a range of issues but the fact remains 
that he has catalyzed an unimaginable amount of change much of it 
exceeding americans wildest dreams 
