search for the body quinn said 
sharp 28 was the 13th known daredevil to challenge the falls 
since 1901 and the fourth to lose his life all previous attempts on 
record have involved barrels or inflated rubber containers 
had sharp survived his trip he would have been subject to a 
10000 canadian fine for attempting an illegal stunt quinn said 
