the tape speaks for itself he said before the trial 
in the 1973 case of miller vs california the us supreme court 
established guidelines for finding material obscene 
the justices ruled that the material must under the contemporary 
standards of individual communities describe sexual conduct in a 
patently offensive way appeal to the prurient interest and lack 
serious artistic literary or political value 
