television might make your brain cry out for 
sustenance but it could be worse for couch potatoes if it inspires 
them to down the same junk they see actors eating on tv shows at 
night 
no kidding thats the opinion of a study that analyzed the food 
content of 11 top network shows and almost burped in dismay 
the primetime diet is inconsistent with dietary guidelines for 
healthy americans says a summation of the study published in 
this months issue of the american journal of public health 
the study conducted in the summer of 1988 was designed to 
examine whether what we see eaten on tv has any impact on what we 
eat could be it concluded however it added this is 
speculative and further research is needed 
but the report makes clear that such goodforyou eats as wheat 
germ apples spinach fish and even the mighty banana get short 
shrift in prime time 
