quality child care while they take college courses 
parents who never learned to read will be able to take classes at 
the school they will be encouraged to come to the library any time 
day or night to spend time with a book with their children 
the school also will be a place where women including teenage 
girls can get quality prenatal care 
school officials envision a community center where people can get 
