about a personality development rally in columbus ohio 
involving a highly successful businessman who had risen from poverty 
asked how he had been so wonderfully successful the 
businessman said he believed in god in himself and in his job and 
had immersed myself in the bible there is wisdom in there in 
order to succeed i needed wisdom 
peale added that the bible is full of wisdom ive lived a long 
time and the bible never once failed me or let me down 
he told of a tiny 4foot11 woman who worked for the late new 
york mayor fiorello la guardia and who once in an elevator 
complained to him she couldnt do much because she was so small 
