to me im going to tell you something and i know what im talking 
about you trust god and believe in yourself and you can do 
anything 
as he left the elevator she noticed that the 5foot2 la guardia 
was short too but as he disappeared down the hall i saw he was 
a giant of a man 
so are you peale told his listeners by trusting god 
following jesus and believing in yourself he said you can do 
anything 
